<p>They have a 60 day guarentee so if yo&#8217;re worried about putting out the $27 for a single user license, or $47 for an unlimited license you can rest assured that you will receive value for your money, not to mention the return on your time yuo will get by targeting the best websites, while learning what messages hit a chord with your audience. These are ONE TIME fees. Check it out at <a title="Social Metrics Pro" href="http://weeklywebtools.com/social-metrics" target="_blank">www.socialmetricspro.com</a></p>
<h2>If This Then That</h2>
<p>This is a hard webstie to classify. It allows you to have an action trigger on another action. For example, if I&#8217;m tagged in a picture on Facebook then send me a text message. It works with all sorts of networks (evernote, facebook, twitter, etc).  Check it out at <a title="If This Then That" href="http://www.ifttt.com" target="_blank">www.ifttt.com</a> (it&#8217;s free).</p>
