			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p><a title="Questions and Answers WordPress Plugin" href="http://weeklywebtools.com/wordpressfaq" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft" style="margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px;" title="wordpress-faqs-plugin" src="http://tribulant.postaffiliatepro.com/accounts/default1/banners/questions-small.jpg" alt="wordpress-faqs-plugin" width="125" height="125" /></a><img style="border: 0;" src="http://tribulant.postaffiliatepro.com/scripts/imp.php?a_aid=jammindave&amp;a_bid=b9082471" alt="" width="1" height="1" />One way that you can boost customer service is by having a frequently asked questions section (FAQ). This is a easy to use plugin that is only $29.99 for a single user liscense. It has great features that you can use to manage questions, and make it easy create a FAQ section on your website. Then you can have your visitors search through the FAQ to get answers. It has a great accordian type interface that amkes it easy to read. Then if they can&#8217;t find the question, there is an easyway for visitors to submit questions. There are notification settings to alert you of a new question.</p>
