		<itunes:summary>I just found out a great Wordpress plugin that records video of your visitors when they are on your site. Want to know why people aren't signing up for that newsletter? Want to know why they are not subscribing to that podcast? Ordering that product? Say goodbye to analytics, and say hello to.....well,,, spying pretty much. This plugin records video of their visit and takes all the guesswork out. Then you can run reports on their activities. It also allows you to create campaigns to track converstions. It's really impressive. When I went to their website, I was sure this was going to be a plugin that had a monthly fee, or something to handle to stress of all these video recordings.

What I found was amazing. The pricing for a single wesbite is $47. If you want it on three websites, it's only $10 more. If you want it on unlmiited websites, it's only $97 which is nothing compared to the insights you will get from this pulgin. This also includes lifetime upgrades. If you're looking for a catch, let me know if you find one as I sure can't find it. For more information go to www.firsttimevisitor.com (http://www.firsttimevisitor.com)

