<h3>Free PDF to Word Converter</h3>
<p>I found a cool tool for converting a PDF document to word format. You simply go to www.pdftoword.com and upload the PDF and enter your email. They send you the word doc. This is from the people who make Nitro Pro a PDf editing tool thats much cheaper than Adobe acrobat. Check it out at <a title="PDF To Word" href="http://www.pdftoword.com" target="_blank">www.pdftoword.com</a></p>
